SUMMARY:The Ravi Iyer Fusion Experience
DESCRIPTION:Ragas and rock have more in common than you think.  \nThis concert is inspired by the idea that different musical traditions can have a conversation rather than exist separately. Classical Hindustani and Carnatic ragas find new breath in this concert.  \nRavi Iyer on guitar\, Anirudha S Bhat on mridangam\, and Rahul Pophali on tabla\, bring the raw energy of rock\, the smooth touch of blues\, and the improvisational spirit of jazz into dialogue. \nTraditions bridged. Melodies reconstructed. \nSupported by:\n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/the-ravi-iyer-fusion-experience/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Music,Performing Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/Thumbnail-21-3.jpg
END:VEVENT
