SUMMARY:Paper Trail
DESCRIPTION:One instrument. One evening. Centuries of music.  \nIn this intimate concert\, Antara Dasgupta will trace the sounds of classical guitar across time and geography. Drawing on etchings by Francisco Goya\, poems by Wilhelm Müller set to music by Franz Schubert\, and Alice in Wonderland\, she uncovers the conversations between music and other expressions of art.  \nMelodies that echo through time\, resounding still\, today.  \nSupported by: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/paper-trail/
LOCATION:7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bengaluru\, Karnataka\, 560 071\, India
CATEGORIES:Music,Performing Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/Thumbnail_PT.jpg
END:VEVENT
